    ...(cand.reason ? { reason: cand.reason } : { reason: 'proposed from prompt' }),
    ...(cand.deckSlot ? { deckSlot: cand.deckSlot } : {}),
  });
}
```

So the `recordId` becomes "96-well plate" (the hint itself) instead of the actual labware definition record ID.

The fixture expects `labwareHint: lbw-def-generic-96-well-plate`. This means the test needs to have a proper `searchLabwareByHint` that returns the correct record ID for "96-well plate".

Let me check if there's a labware definition registry that I can use:

